## How to upload

1. Save each file to the `recommended_save_path` exactly as listed.
2. After upload, re-run phase 1.5 (`context_setup`) in `living_update` mode — the curator will detect the new files, sha256 them, and write per-file manifests.
3. Confirm in the next session-close summary that `pending_user_uploads` has decreased.

## Notes

- Default `confidence_pct_when_uploaded_default = 80` for `user_uploaded_doc`. Override during the post-upload HITL.
- The AI will not fetch on its own; this list is the only path for inaccessible sources.
- If a recommended source is no longer needed, mark it as `[OBSOLETE]` in the description and re-run phase 1.5; the row will be moved to `context/archive/`.
